article.linkText: Bello scores 29 in Purdue Fort Wayne's 86-64 victory against Texas A&M-Commerce
article.story: FORT WAYNE, Ind. -- — Rasheed Bello had 29 points in Purdue Fort Wayne's 86-64 win over Texas A&M-Commerce on Sunday. Bello was 10 of 18 shooting, including 3 for 3 from 3-point range, and went 6 for 7 from the line for the Mastodons (3-0). Anthony Roberts added 17 points and 10 rebounds. Jerome Brewer Jr. led the Lions (0-4) with 13 points and Kalen Williams added 10 points. Purdue Fort Wayne's next game is Friday against Northern Arizona. Texas A&M-Commerce hosts USAO on Wednesday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
